━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  HOW THE ANALYSIS WORKS (No AI/API)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  The engine uses rule-based scoring:

  KEYWORD MATCHING
  Each domain has a curated list of 15–20 must-have keywords
  and 20–25 nice-to-have keywords. The engine checks which
  are present in your resume text and scores accordingly.

  ATS AUDIT
  12 rules checked:  contact info, email, experience section,
  education section, skills section, bullet points, dates,
  no tables, appropriate length, action verbs, quantified
  achievements, no personal pronouns.

  SCORING FORMULA
  Overall = Experience(25%) + Skills(25%) + Education(15%)
           + Presentation(15%) + Relevance(10%) + ATS(10%)

  SALARY DATA
  Pre-built market ranges per domain × experience level,
  based on 2024 industry compensation surveys.

