  Mac / Linux:
    cd ~/Downloads/ResumeScreener-Pro
    python3 -m http.server 8080
    open http://localhost:8080

  Windows (PowerShell):
    cd C:\Users\YourName\Downloads\ResumeScreener-Pro
    python -m http.server 8080
    start http://localhost:8080

